OL,3,CSussex hospices fears services will be
OL,4,Ccut if government funding fails
OL,6,FThat could put more pressure on other
OL,7,Fparts of the healthcare system.
OL,9,F"Hospices play a vital role of keeping
OL,10,Fpeople out of hospital," he said. "A&E
OL,11,Fwill be busier and unfortunately
OL,12,Fpeople will be dying in hospitals or
OL,13,Fthey'll be dying in corridors."
OL,15,FHospices have come under increasing
OL,16,Ffinancial pressure in recent years due
OL,17,Fto rising inflation and challenges
OL,18,Frecruiting staff.
