OL,3,CSussex hospices fears services will be
OL,4,Ccut if government funding fails
OL,6,FIn December 2024, the government
OL,7,Fannounced an extra #100m for the
OL,8,Fsector, but this will only cover the
OL,9,Fcost of improving facilities and will
OL,10,Fnot go towards day-to-day care.
OL,12,F"We're being squeezed from all sides,"
OL,13,FPalma said. "National insurance costs
OL,14,F#600,000 alone for us this year. The
OL,15,Fcost of living cost on people is
OL,16,Fsqueezing them to give less."
