OL,3,CSussex hospices fears services will be
OL,4,Ccut if government funding fails
OL,6,F"We're in a position here in the group
OL,7,Fthat services will continue to run at
OL,8,Fleast over the next few years. But if
OL,9,Fthere is no further government funding
OL,10,For settlement for us we will
OL,11,Fabsolutely have to start looking at
OL,12,Freducing those services."
OL,14,FShaun, who is receiving end-of-life
OL,15,Fcare at St Barnabas, said the hospice
OL,16,Fhas provided invaluable support in his
OL,17,Ffinal months.
