OL,3,CSussex hospices fears services will be
OL,4,Ccut if government funding fails
OL,6,F"When I was told that I might have
OL,7,Fonly three months to live, it wasn't a
OL,8,Fsurprise but of course it was a huge
OL,9,Fshock," he said.
OL,11,F"The second time I went to St
OL,12,FBarnabas, I broke down. And I will
OL,13,Fnever forget the patient, loving
OL,14,Fkindness, the compassion with which I
OL,15,Fwas cherished that day.
OL,17,F"In a nutshell that's what St Barnabas
OL,18,Fdoes, it cherishes people in the last
OL,19,Fphase of their life and it's beyond
OL,20,Fprice."
