OL,3,CSussex hospices fears services will be
OL,4,Ccut if government funding fails
OL,6,FLouise Humphrey, Palliative Heart
OL,7,FFailure Specialist Nurse who cares for
OL,8,FShaun, said: "If a patient is well-
OL,9,Fsupported at the end of their life by
OL,10,Fpeople who have a specialism in
OL,11,Fpalliative care, or hospice care, it
OL,12,Fgives that patient and their family,
OL,13,Ftheir loved ones, an opportunity to
OL,14,Freally home in on and enjoy the time
OL,15,Fthat they have left together."
OL,17,FThe Department for Health told ITV it
OL,18,F"recognises the incredible work that
OL,19,Fhospices do across the country."
