OL,6,FIt added: "Through our 10 Year Health
OL,7,FPlan, we are working to make sure the
OL,8,Fpalliative and end of life care sector
OL,9,Fis sustainable as we shift more
OL,10,Fhealthcare out of hospitals and into
OL,11,Fthe community.
OL,13,F"Our #100 million investment to
OL,14,Fimprove hospice facilities is the
OL,15,Fbiggest in a generation, and NHS
OL,16,FEngland is providing #26 million for
OL,17,Fchildren and young people's hospices."
